<section style="padding-left: 8vw;padding-top: 5vw;">
  <p style="font: 400 1.3em 'Raleway', sans-serif;color: #333;"><h1>
  Hi, <%= @user.name %>!
</h1>
  </p>

  <p style="font: 400 1.1em 'Raleway', sans-serif;color: #333; line-height: 35px;">
    We received a request to change your email address to this one for <a href="https://makerepo.com">MakerRepo.com</a>.
    <br>
    If you did ask for this change, please click on the following <%= link_to "link", confirm_edited_email_users_url(email_token: @email_hash, user_token: @user_hash) %> to process this change. <br>
    If the link isn't working, try copy/pasting the following address : <%= confirm_edited_email_users_url(email_token: @email_hash, user_token: @user_hash) %>
    <br>
    If you did not request this change, you do not have to do anything.
  </p>


  <p style="  font: 400 1.1em 'Raleway', sans-serif;color: #333;">
    Cheers,<br>
    The MakerRepo Team
  </p>
</section>
